# Claude Skills Reference for SkillSpark

This project utilizes skills from the [Awesome Claude Skills](https://github.com/ComposioHQ/awesome-claude-skills) repository to enhance AI capabilities.

## Development & Code Tools

- **test-driven-development**: Use when implementing features or bugfixes
- **software-architecture**: Design patterns (Clean Architecture, SOLID principles)
- **artifacts-builder**: Reference for design patterns, shadcn/ui component usage, and TailwindCSS best practices
- **prompt-engineering**: Design and optimize prompts for multi-LLM integration
- **mcp-builder**: Build MCP servers for LLM orchestration

## Document Processing (Teacher Features)

- **docx**: Generate Word documents (worksheets, lesson plans)
- **pdf**: Generate PDF exam papers, extract text from uploaded files
- **pptx**: Generate presentations for teachers
- **xlsx**: Generate spreadsheets for grading

## Data & Analysis

- **postgres**: Execute safe SQL queries against PostgreSQL database
- **deep-research**: Research for educational content generation

## Communication & Writing

- **content-research-writer**: Generate educational content, assist with content creation
- **meeting-insights-analyzer**: Analyze student-teacher interactions
- **brainstorming**: Transform ideas into feature designs

## Creative & Media (Design System)

- **canvas-design**: Create visual assets and cute UI elements
- **theme-factory**: Apply cute themes to design system
- **image-enhancer**: Enhance uploaded images, process homework images

## Productivity & Organization

- **file-organizer**: Organize uploaded homework files, manage submissions
- **tailored-resume-generator**: Generate personalized learning paths

## Skills Usage by Feature

- **Teacher Artifact Generation**: `docx`, `pptx`, `xlsx`, `pdf`
- **Teacher Exam Paper Generation**: `docx`, `pdf`, `prompt-engineering`
- **AI Chat Interfaces**: `content-research-writer`, `brainstorming`
- **Document Processing**: `pdf`, `docx` (for text extraction)
- **UI Development**: `artifacts-builder` (design patterns & shadcn/ui), `canvas-design`, `theme-factory`
- **Database Operations**: `postgres`
- **Code Quality**: `test-driven-development`, `software-architecture`

